snippet.title: Embr Consoles Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase
snippet.description:
A brand new trailer for Embr, a frantic firefighting game set in a hyper-capitalist reality where traditional emergency services are a thing of the past. Scale buildings, smash windows, fight fires and save lives either solo or co-op in up to teams of four. Embr is the last stand in a world ablaze.

Nmbr is coming to consoles (PS4, Xbox One, Switch, PC) and has Cross play support

Launching Summer 2021

#Embr
